    "description": "We're on a mission to make cooking times shorter and eating time longer. We love this simple method for cooking fish. You just tap it in flour and pan-fry. We've taken this dish to Thailand and served with hot basmati rice and a classic Thai green curry sauce with mushrooms, spring onion and coriander. Ready in 20!",
